# Game Systems Guide

Canonical sources: `docs/GAME_SYSTEM_MAP.md`, `docs/player-systems-guide.md`, `1Developer/AktiviteOzeti.md`. This file is a **quick reference** for agents.

---

## 1. Time System

**Owner:** `passages/0 - System/Widgets/TimeWidgets.twee` + `variablesTime.twee`

**Variable:** `$timeSys` = `{ year, month, day, hour, minute, period }`
- `period`: `"morning" | "afternoon" | "evening" | "night"` (derived)

**Advance time:**
```twee
<<advanceTime N>>            /* N minutes */
```
Side effects: updates character locations (`<<updateCharacterLocations>>`), decays needs/skills/relationships, triggers schedule events.

**Read current time:** `$timeSys.hour`, `$timeSys.period`, `$timeSys.day`

---

## 2. Stats System

**Owner:** `StatCalculator.twee` (derivation), `StatNotifications.twee` (toasts), `variablesBase.twee` (storage)

**Main stats:** (stored on `$character` or dedicated `$stats`)
- `confidence`, `charisma`, `intelligence`, `strength`, `endurance`
- `attractiveness` (derived from body + wardrobe)
- `corruption` (quest-gated)

**Derived/bounded:** `energy`, `health`, `mood`, `hunger`, `thirst`, `bladder`, `hygiene`

**Modify stats:**
```twee
<<gainStat "confidence" 5>>
<<loseStat "energy" 10>>
```
These show notifications and clamp to valid ranges.

**Derivations:** `StatCalculator.twee` recomputes on passage render via `<<updateDerivedStats>>`.

---

## 3. Needs System

**Owner:** `NeedsSystem.twee`

Hunger/thirst/bladder/hygiene decay per `<<advanceTime>>`. When a need crosses threshold, mood/energy drops. Activities restore them:
- Eat restaurant/food → hunger
- Drink → thirst
- Bathroom (`parkWC`, home bathroom) → bladder
- Shower → hygiene

---

## 4. Quest System V2

**Owner:** `passages/5 - QuestSystem/`

**Key objects:**
- `setup.quests[questId]` — static definition (title, stages, requirements, onComplete)
- `$activeQuests` — currently active quest IDs
- `$questState[questId]` — per-quest runtime state (current stage, objectives done, flags)
- `$completedQuests` — finished quest IDs

**Quest schema** (see `QuestDatabase_Base.twee` comment block):
```
stages: [{
  id, title, desc,
  triggers: { location, time, character, flag },
  forceScene: bool, passage: "target",
  objectives: [{ id, text, trigger }],
  completeWhen: "allObjectives" | "anyObjective"
}]
```

**Widgets:** `<<questPrompts>>`, `<<advanceQuestStage>>`, `<<completeQuest>>`, `<<setQuestFlag>>`

**Current quest chain:** First Shopping → Find Job → Check Old Town → (more queued). Full list in `1Developer/ozetler/Quest-Pasaj-Stat-Zaman-Ozeti.md`.

---

## 5. Character / Relationship System

**Owner:** `CharacterWidgets.twee`, per-character init in `Init/characters/`

**Variable:** `$characters[charId]` = `{ name, currentLocation, currentStatus, schedule, appearance, ... }`
- `currentStatus`: `"available" | "sleeping" | "showering" | "working" | "busy"`

**Relationships:** `$relationships[charId]` = `{ love, friendship, respect, lust, trust, ... }`

**Update location:** `<<updateCharacterLocations>>` runs schedule for current time.

**Decay:** `RelationshipDecay.twee` runs daily.

---

## 6. Wardrobe System

**Owner:** `wardrobeWidget.twee`, `0 - System/WardrobeSys/`

**Variable:** `$wardrobe.equipped` = slot-keyed item IDs (top, bottom, panties, bra, shoes, etc.)

**Checks:**
- `exposureLevel` — derived 0-100, drives corruption gates
- `durability`, `dirt` — per-item, tracked across days

**Widgets:** `<<equipOutfit>>`, `<<wardrobeCheckExposure>>`, `<<changeIntoPajamas>>`

**Modal UI:** `assets/system/js/modal/character.js` → Outfit tab

---

## 7. Phone System

**Owner:** `passages/0 - System/Widgets/PhoneWidgets.twee` + `assets/system/js/ui/phone/`

**State:** `$phoneConversations`, `$phoneContactsUnlocked`, `$phoneCallsLog`, `$phoneAppointments`, `$phoneFotogramDMs`

**Apps:** Messages, Contacts, Calendar, Fotogram (social), Finder (dating), Camera, Gallery

**Widgets:**
- `<<phoneSendMessage charId text>>`
- `<<phoneStartConversation charId firstMsg>>`
- `<<phoneWhereAreYou charId>>` (auto-reply based on schedule)
- `<<phoneCreateAppointment charId location hour>>`
- `<<phoneUnlockContact charId>>`

**JS:** `window.PhoneAPI` (set in `phone/index.js`), `window.phoneViewState` (mutable sub-app state)

---

## 8. Job System

**Owner:** `JobWidgets.twee`, `JobDatabase.twee`, `passages/7 - Work/`

**Variable:** `$jobs[jobId]` = `{ tier, shifts, earnings, experience }`

**Flow:** Apply → first shift → promote tiers → earn wage + experience. Stats decay during shift (energy -, confidence +).

**Definitions:** See `1Developer/CheatSheets/JobSystemDesign.md` for tier structure.

---

## 9. Map / Navigation

**Owner:** `assets/system/js/ui/map.js`, `variablesMap.twee`, `setup.navCards`

**Discovery:** `$discovered[locationId]` — location visible on map only after discovery flag set.

**Fast travel:** `passages/8 - Others/fastTravelTaxi.twee` (costs money + time).

---

## 10. Save / Load

**Owner:** `assets/system/js/modal/saveload.js`, SugarCube built-in `Save` API

**Auto-save:** slot 0, on `:passageend` event.

**Migration:** `0 - System/Migrations/` — runs on load if `$saveVersion` < current.

---

## System Interconnections (Quick Graph)

```
<<advanceTime>>
  ├─► updateCharacterLocations (CharacterWidgets)
  ├─► decay needs       (NeedsSystem)
  ├─► decay skills      (SkillDecay)
  ├─► decay relations   (RelationshipDecay)
  ├─► trigger schedule events
  └─► ambient events    (HubAmbientWidgets)

:passagerender (JS event)
  ├─► location.js      → background image
  ├─► layout.js        → wrap content
  ├─► topbar.js        → refresh badges
  ├─► rightbar.js      → refresh stats
  └─► StatCalculator   → derived stats

Quest stage trigger
  ├─► requirements check (location, time, character, flags)
  ├─► forceScene → <<goto>>
  ├─► objectives tracked
  └─► onComplete → stats/money/flags/nextQuest
```

